title: S5 Ep56: Backstage at BAM19: Which priorities for the new EU leadership?
itunes:title: Backstage at BAM19: Which priorities for the new EU leadership?
description: When the last Commission took office in 2014, Europe was consumed by the eurozone crisis. Today, the incoming leadership must decide how to deal with a variety of issues. In this podcast, Rebecca Christie discusses the priorities for the new EU leadership, with Guntram Wolff.
itunes:author: Bruegel
